---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service — Explore Singapore"
  description="Terms of Service for Explore Singapore. Read our terms governing the use of our free AI-powered trip planner."
>
  <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-[#f0f0f0]">
    <div class="max-w-[1120px] mx-auto px-6 h-[64px] flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <div class="w-7 h-7 rounded-md bg-[#EF3340] flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 256 256" fill="white"><path d="M128,16a88.1,88.1,0,0,0-88,88c0,75.3,80,132.17,83.36,134.55a8,8,0,0,0,9.28,0C136,236.17,216,179.3,216,104A88.1,88.1,0,0,0,128,16Zm0,56a32,32,0,1,1-32,32A32,32,0,0,1,128,72Z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="text-[16px] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a]">Explore <span class="text-[#EF3340]">Singapore</span></span>
      </a>
      <a href="/" class="text-[13px] text-[#888] hover:text-[#1a1a1a] transition-colors">Back to home</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-[28px] font-bold text-[#111] mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-[14px] text-[#888] mb-10">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-[20px] font-bold text-[#111] mb-3">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed mb-3">
        By accessing or using Explore Singapore ("the Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the Service.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed">
        These terms apply to all visitors, users, and others who access the Service, whether through our website at exploresg.info or the associated web application at app.exploresg.info.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-[20px] font-bold text-[#111] mb-3">Service Description</h2>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed mb-3">
        Explore Singapore is a free, browser-based trip planning tool that helps users discover places in Singapore, create personalised itineraries, and plan their visits. The Service includes:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed space-y-1 mb-3">
        <li>A curated directory of 100+ places in Singapore</li>
        <li>An AI-powered itinerary planner</li>
        <li>Interactive maps and navigation links</li>
        <li>Exportable trip plans in PDF format</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed">
        The Service is provided free of charge. No account creation or payment is required.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-[20px] font-bold text-[#111] mb-3">User Conduct</h2>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed mb-3">
        When using the Service, you agree not to:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed space-y-1 mb-3">
        <li>Use the Service for any unlawful purpose or in violation of any applicable laws</li>
        <li>Attempt to interfere with, compromise, or disrupt the Service or its infrastructure</li>
        <li>Use automated scripts, bots, or scrapers to access the Service in a manner that degrades performance for other users</li>
        <li>Reverse engineer, decompile, or attempt to extract the source code of proprietary components</li>
        <li>Misrepresent your identity or affiliation when interacting with the Service</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed">
        We reserve the right to restrict access to the Service for any user who violates these terms.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-[20px] font-bold text-[#111] mb-3">Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed mb-3">
        All content, design, branding, and code comprising the Service are owned by Explore Singapore or its licensors and are protected by applicable intellectual property laws.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed mb-3">
        You may use the Service for personal, non-commercial trip planning purposes. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works from our content, branding, or proprietary materials without prior written permission.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed">
        Itineraries and trip plans you create using the Service are yours. We claim no ownership over user-generated content.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-[20px] font-bold text-[#111] mb-3">Disclaimers</h2>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed mb-3">
        The Service is provided on an "as is" and "as available" basis without warranties of any kind, either express or implied.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed mb-3">
        <strong>Travel information may change.</strong> While we strive to keep our place data accurate and up to date, we cannot guarantee that all information — including opening hours, prices, availability, or operational status of venues — is current at the time of your visit. We strongly recommend verifying details directly with venues before visiting.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed">
        AI-generated itineraries are suggestions based on available data and algorithms. They should be treated as starting points for your planning, not as guaranteed or verified travel advice.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-[20px] font-bold text-[#111] mb-3">Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed mb-3">
        To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, Explore Singapore and its operators shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, including but not limited to:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed space-y-1 mb-3">
        <li>Loss of profits, data, or goodwill</li>
        <li>Travel disruptions or expenses arising from reliance on information provided by the Service</li>
        <li>Service interruptions or data loss</li>
        <li>Any damages arising from third-party services or external links</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed">
        Our total liability for any claim arising from or related to the Service shall not exceed SGD $0, reflecting the free nature of the Service.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-[20px] font-bold text-[#111] mb-3">Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed mb-3">
        We reserve the right to modify these Terms of Service at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting to this page. The "Last updated" date at the top of this page indicates when these terms were most recently revised.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed">
        Your continued use of the Service after any changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms. We encourage you to review these terms periodically.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-[20px] font-bold text-[#111] mb-3">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[#555] leading-relaxed">
        If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@exploresg.info" class="text-[#0066cc] hover:underline">hello@exploresg.info</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="border-t border-[#eee] bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-6 py-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <p class="text-[13px] text-[#999]">&copy; 2026 Explore Singapore. All rights reserved.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <a href="/privacy" class="text-[13px] text-[#666] hover:text-[#111] transition-colors">Privacy</a>
        <a href="/terms" class="text-[13px] text-[#666] hover:text-[#111] transition-colors">Terms</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
